rows.label: tlk41400021_04_msg0001
rows.name:
Have you heard of Woodboards?!
You've gotta get into Woodboards!
Everyone's talking about them!

rows.label: tlk41400021_04_msg0002
rows.name:
By combining advanced Superbian tech
with Puzzletree Wood from Gula,
a new musical instrument was born!

rows.label: tlk41400021_04_msg0003
rows.name:
Thanks to the supreme flexibility of
Puzzletree Wood, this new instrument
produces tones like an angelic chorus!

rows.label: tlk41400021_04_msg0004
rows.name:
And it's called...the Woodboard!
I named it myself, by the way.

rows.label: tlk41400021_04_msg0005
rows.name:
It's like a keyboard made of wood, so...
Woodboard! I'm a genius, right?
